data.description: Country living at its best! Ideal horse property, fenced and cross fenced, 2 pastures of terraced land. Spacious 4 BR, 3BA, 2 living areas,and sunny country kitchen with center island and breakfast bar. Front porch and huge back deck to enjoy sunrises. Updated fixtures, flooring and carpet. Move in and enjoy the peaceful life of the country!
